Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃，那个...\N要说什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...!要保持房间明亮\N坐远一点再看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?叫我到这里来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.82,0:00:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的话\N就把这穿上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行的话，就这样放着\N离开也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.35,0:00:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面 麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.59,0:00:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等了好久呢，岩城同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.73,0:01:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我菜搞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜，菜搞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.54,0:01:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.47,0:01:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公 老公 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起来了吗，老公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.22,0:01:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易又到了\N重要的地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学校 要迟到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.76,0:01:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛一大清早就在傻笑啊\N乱恶心一把的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘．密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了也还是\N好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸\N也依然是那么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.54,0:01:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.45,0:02:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧\N一起来吧 一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.72,0:02:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一．起．来．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.49,0:02:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那天以来的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.07,0:02:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都希望能感觉的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管到哪里都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管做什么都好让人心动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷入恋爱的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都好像魔法师一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以让人高兴起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.53,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了也还是\N好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸\N也依然是那么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧\N一起来吧 一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功!我们一起去了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不到放弃的时候吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是说已经正式结婚了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.71,0:03:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家早啊\N早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有些突然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.74,0:03:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我们有一位新同学要加入喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.69,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就是从今天起成为我们班上\N一份子的岩城莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师，那孩子不是小学生吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宾果~完全正确!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师，她明明是小学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么可以来国中上课呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然才12岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过她可是跳级编进来的呢\N对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不太清楚\N好像就是那样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请大家多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是国家权力吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，找到老公了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么什么\N老公是在叫谁啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，是在叫岩城吗?\N谁是你老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是怎么一回事啊\N岩城同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我没有关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不是连入籍\N都办好了吗 看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要想歪了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是那家伙自己随便乱说的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~\N叫人嫉妒勒~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就可以整天在一起了\N老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面确实是写着\N“妻子”呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管它上面有写没写\N反正我跟那家伙一点关系也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌\N干嘛那么认真嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.02,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,15岁和12岁怎么可能\N结的了婚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真了不起\N好像是真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是真的啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不出来你还是个小捣蛋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，莉采儿的\N座位在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公的旁边~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对，在圣本同学的旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里喔，这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在那里闹别扭\N听老师的话!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.97,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是~ 可是为什么不行呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是能坐老公旁边就好了说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是圣本葵，请多指教喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，是!请你多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然没能坐在一起会有些寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过从这里看岩城同学\N看得很清楚唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.36,0:05:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，好大的包袱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那装了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿...秘密!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 嗯\N太好了 太好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咱们先来祝贺\N莉采儿踏出新的旅程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，真不错\N是纯生米酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，干爹们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔喔，莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制服很适合你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你长大了呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位是莉采儿的监护人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我们也是转学生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们怎么看都是中学生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，耶~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不关我的事...\N不关我的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然还是不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，拿清酒庆祝是过份了些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该用甜酒之类的吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油吧，莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我我我我~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿想作答吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是\N请让老公来作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.91,0:06:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家想看老公\N帅气作答的样子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死啦~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很想看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学\N“帅气作答的样子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就决定岩城同学罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定了 决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个虽然蛮难的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过岩城同学的话\N应该答的出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就帮大家做个示范吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去!真没办法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公\N太帅了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 加油吧\N老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燃烧吧 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿!我的老公最棒了，不管...\N给我安分一点~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那在搞什么飞机啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?我是想帮老公打打气...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有哪个世界的人\N会在教室里做那种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可是，那种打气的方法\N是我在图书馆查到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看的是哪个\N图书馆的哪本书啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊哈，第一次被老公用头顶耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听好!在学校别黏着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然回家以后别想要我理你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次被老公\N用胶带黏起来耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿那家伙没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是没关系 今天有准备了\N让他大吃一惊的好东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿~ 是什么是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿，是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么还不快点到中午呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了准备那个整夜都没有睡\N好困喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.28,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是...那个穿小熊内...\N那白色东西的女孩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我\N就仿佛被命运的闪电击中一般...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.65,0:08:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女孩一定是为了我而生\N为了我而来到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个让他大吃一惊的\N好东西是什么?告诉我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要说呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,圣本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能耽误点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤凰院同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午....午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一位是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...那个\N她是今....今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转....转入我们班的\N莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，这没有什么...\N啊~实在是太耀眼了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次跟憧憬的\N凤凰院同学说到话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我真的是太~幸运了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面\N我的名字是凤凰院龙之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然这么说\N或许有些失礼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的倩影便深深地映在我的\N眼眸之中想忘也忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就如同是我理想中的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一定是在神的引导之下\N才会如此的在这里相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了纪念我俩的相识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道这个周末，是否有荣幸\N请你来家里接受我的招待呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能答应\N真的是太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，就衷心期待\N你的光临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.69,0:09:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最钟爱的少女啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的\N想说你怎么还不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果是在走廊上睡着了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.61,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事 没事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是到保健室\N睡一下比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题 没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快到中午了\N我想先让肚子空一点才很努力跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.72,0:09:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公再等一下喔~\N等、等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害!\N你花了一整夜在作便当啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.51,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从妈妈那里听了好多老公爱吃的东西\N都不知道要做哪些才好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，能不能让我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦\N人家会不好意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，只能眯一下喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~ 好丰盛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿\N谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.39,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的做的很棒呢，这个就算是\N岩城同学看了也一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗?\N没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.16,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~ 老公会很高兴~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这啥啊!\N老妈也太混了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起吃中饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.31,0:10:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰唆!就说不要黏过来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经...不能吃了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、我可不是故意的啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊?那可是莉采儿熬夜为你做的\N这样太过份了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系啦，小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要再重做就好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿? 莉采儿!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公，味道怎么样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那还用说，当然好吃嘛\N太好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去...真是个给人添麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是我的便当\N干嘛熬夜去做 笨蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，学校呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就放学啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.52,0:12:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是老公送我回来的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~你不要搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是事情都发生了\N没有办法才会这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算说我们同班\N以后也不会跟你一起上学啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，别再为了\N做个便当熬夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.37,0:12:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?\N人家还想每天帮你做便当的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你鸡婆啦\N白痴~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人和女人真是难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了查清楚我去了图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.83,0:13:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家好喜欢他\N所以我不会哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.74,0:13:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不气馁，不逃避\N更不会失去勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.81,0:13:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信总有一天春天会到来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.59,0:13:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿出认真的力量\N认真的力量向前冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
