Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟岩城同学的关系?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌，我跟他就只是\N儿时玩伴而已啦
