Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小的时候住在丹治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是那个时候的邻居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别看他那个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前他可是个\N既听话又开朗的孩子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一提\N不知道什么时候变成了那副德行...
